docker-wattsi
~~~~~~~~~~~~~

|Dockerfile|s for Wattsi and html-build.

* Usage

  $ docker pull wakaba/docker-wattsi:html-build && \
    docker run -v `pwd`/output:/html-build/output \
               -v `pwd`/html:/html-build/html \
               -i -t wakaba/docker-wattsi:html-build ./build.sh

  $ docker pull wakaba/docker-wattsi:wattsi && \
    docker run -i wakaba/docker-wattsi:wattsi wattsi ...

* Repository

GitHub <https://github.com/wakaba/docker-wattsi>.

Docker Hub <https://registry.hub.docker.com/u/wakaba/docker-wattsi/>.

* See also

<https://github.com/whatwg/wattsi>
<https://github.com/whatwg/html-build>
<https://github.com/whatwg/html>

